PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774195867
OL,3,CCollege student has suspected
OL,4,Cmeningitis but the risk to others is
OL,5,C'very low'
OL,7,FA North West sixth form college has
OL,8,Fmoved to reassure students and parents
OL,9,Fafter a suspected case of meningitis
OL,10,Fwas reported on campus.
OL,12,FIt comes as the number of cases of
OL,13,Fmeningitis linked to an outbreak in
OL,14,FKent rose to 34.
OL,16,FSt John Rigby College, in Orrell,
OL,17,FWigan, confirmed on Friday (20 March)
OL,18,Fit had been advised by the UK Health
OL,19,FSecurity Agency that a single student
OL,20,Fis being treated as a suspected
OL,21,Fmeningococcal case.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774195867
OL,3,CCollege student has suspected
OL,4,Cmeningitis but the risk to others is
OL,5,C'very low'
OL,7,FThe college stressed that only one
OL,8,Fcase has been identified and that
OL,9,Fthere is no known link to the
OL,10,Fsituation in Kent.
OL,12,FHealth authorities have already
OL,13,Fcarried out contact tracing,
OL,14,Fidentifying close contacts and
OL,15,Foffering them precautionary
OL,16,Fantibiotics, the college said.
OL,18,FThe college said that anyone who has
OL,19,Fnot been directly contacted does not
OL,20,Frequire treatment and that the overall
OL,21,Frisk to students remains very low.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774195867
OL,3,CCollege student has suspected
OL,4,Cmeningitis but the risk to others is
OL,5,C'very low'
OL,7,FAcross England, approximately one case
OL,8,Fof meningitis is reported each day,
OL,9,Fand health professionals are managing
OL,10,Fthe situation in Wigan in line with
OL,11,Fstandard procedures.
OL,13,FStudents have been advised there is no
OL,14,Fneed to stay off college or alter
OL,15,Ftheir usual activities.
OL,17,FThe college added that it acted
OL,18,Fswiftly in response to the case and
OL,19,Fcontinues to work closely with health
OL,20,Fofficials to monitor the situation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
