FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774195867
OL,3,CCollege student has suspected
OL,4,Cmeningitis but the risk to others is
OL,5,C'very low'
OL,7,FA statement on its website said: "We
OL,8,Fhave been advised by the UK Health
OL,9,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA) that a student
OL,10,Fwho attends this college has recently
OL,11,Fbeen reported as a suspected
OL,12,Fmeningococcal case, which we
OL,13,Funderstand will be concerning,
OL,14,Fespecially in light on the ongoing
OL,15,Fsituation in Kent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
