OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774195867
OL,3,CCollege student has suspected
OL,4,Cmeningitis but the risk to others is
OL,5,C'very low'
OL,7,F"We would like to reassure you that we
OL,8,Fhave acted quickly and there is only
OL,9,Fone suspected case at the college.
OL,10,FHealth agencies have completed contact
OL,11,Ftracing and there is no known
OL,12,Fconnection to the situation in Kent.
OL,14,FAll close contacts of this case have
OL,15,Fbeen identified already and offered
OL,16,Fantibiotics as a precaution.
OL,18,F"No one who has not already been
OL,19,Fidentified and contacted needs
OL,20,Fantibiotics.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
