PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774195867
OL,3,CCollege student has suspected
OL,4,Cmeningitis but the risk to others is
OL,5,C'very low'
OL,7,F"The risk to students at this time is
OL,8,Fvery low.
OL,10,F"There is no need for anyone to remain
OL,11,Foff college or not continue with usual
OL,12,Factivities."
OL,14,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,15,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,16,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,17,Four region.
